&lt;div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sunset at Daman:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On the west coast, the sunset can be a marvelous treat for weary eyes and tired spirits. In Daman, head to the seaside to watch the sun&amp;#8217;s gradual descent over the horizon. If you are lucky (as we were), you will witness a spectacular show.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div id=&#34;attachment_4081&#34; style=&#34;width: 710px&#34; class=&#34;wp-caption alignnone&#34;&gt;
